      <title>谷歌在欧盟法庭上赢得 15 亿欧元罚款之战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/google-wins-eu-court-fight-over-1-5-billion-ad-abuse-fine</link>
